              %li.logged_out.login_status{"data-oahu-display"=>'disconnected'}
                %a.login_btn{:href=>'#', "data-oahu-display"=>'disconnected', "data-oahu-action"=>"connect", "data-oahu-provider"=>"facebook"} Login

            %ul.nav.pull-right
              %li
                %a{:href=>'#product'} Product
              %li
                %a{:href=>'clients'} Clients
              %li
                %a{:href=>'contact'} Contact
              %li
                %a{:href=>'jobs'} Jobs
              / %li
              /   %a.contact{:href=>'mailto:contact@oahu.fr'} contact@oahu.fr


    #page.container
      .hero-unit
        %h1
          Connect with your audience,
          %em anywhere
        %h2
          Oahu creates long term, meaningful relationships
          %br
          between you and your community
          
      %section#product
        .page-header
          %h1 Product
        .row
          .span3
            %h2
              Oahu is an integrated
              %br
              marketing platform.
            that enables you to build richer, more engaging campaigns. Be assured that your campaign is optimized for engagement.

          .span3.offset1
            %h2 Simple to use
            %p 
              Publish our pre-built apps to instantly offer your fans Quizzes, Instant Wins, branded pages and more. You can build entire campaigns without a single line of code

          .span3.offset1
            %h2 Full service
            %p We handle the media, games mechanics, and user generated contents that make your campaigns richer and more compelling.

        .row
          .span3
            %h2 Rich realtime api
            %p Use a robust set of rich realtime push components to create even more ambitious campaigns at a fraction of the time and cost.

          .span3.offset1
            %h2 Complete Metrics
            %p With integrated metrics, Oahu enables you to get a precise overview of how your campaignâ€™s doing, whoâ€™s playing, whoâ€™s sharing and much, much more.

