            %h2 Cross campaign marketing
            %p Most importantly, We do all of this and more with an easy to use single sign-on, that enables your fans to enrich their profile campaign after campaign, allowing you to offer them precisely what makes them tick 

      %section#testdrive{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected'}
        .page-header
          %h1 Test Oahu right here
        .row
          .span4
            %h2 Test out the main Oahu features
            %p
              Since you're connected to Oahu, here's a few simple features you can immediately test out.
              %br
              Many more are available.
            .connect
              %a.btn{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected', "data-oahu-action"=>'disconnect'} Disconnect
          .span4.logged_in{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected'}
            %h2
              Welcome,
              %span.username{"data-oahu-bind"=>'name'} 
            %p 
              %span.oahu_friendscount 0
              of your friends are using Oahu
            .share
              %a.btn{"data-oahu-action"=>"ui.share", "data-oahu-provider"=>"facebook"} Share your love
          .span4.logged_in{"data-oahu-display"=>'connected'}
            %h2 Your recent activity
            .activity{"data-oahu-bind"=>'activity'}


      %section
        .row
          .span4
            #clients.page-header
              %h1 Clients
            %ul.clients
              %li.universal Universal
              %li.pathe PathÃ©
